ComicInfo.Summary:
BIG 20Th ANNIVERSARY SPECIAL!! It's been twenty years of great Femforce fun, action and excitement, and to celebrate, longtime fan favorite Brad Gorby has written this 40-page, book length spectacular all-new, never-before -seen story: "www.derfuerherdownload.com "!! Lady Luger and Fritz Voltzmann are back, with a plan to bring their favorite kind of Fascism back to sweep the globe!! And- they've recruited several of their best Aryan buddies to help them pull it off- Valkyra, Ironjaw and-- The Frightenstein Monster?? This blockbuster saga is chock full of guest-stars, like Firebeam, The Scarlet Scorpion and The Justice Squad (Atoman, Carbonator, Lady Darkness, Beamer and Speedbolt- you remember them), and STILL only tells half the story, as this adventure is TOO BIG to be contained in one issue, it will be continued and concluded in FF #131. This epic is told in chapters, with pencil art on each by a different Femforce favorite artist- Scott Nemmers, Ed Coutts, Don Secrease and Gorby HIMSELF each draw a chapter, but Jaunty Jeff Austin is so good, we had to have him draw TWO!! Inks over most of the book are by the team of Mark and Stephanie Heike, with special individual chapters inked by Austin, Coutts, and Bossman Bill Black. All this encasec in a superb wraparound cover drawn by Da Gorbster, and inked and colored by Mark 'n Steph Heike. What more could you want?
